## Coding Best Practices

- Implement server actions for all backend logic.
- Separate logic into distinct files if a single file exceeds 300 lines of code to enhance maintainability and readability.
- Encapsulate client-side logic within React hooks.
- Ensure separation of HTML structure from client-side logic.
- Adhere strictly to the SOLID and DRY principles in all coding activities.
- The layout implementation shall consistently utilize ShadcnUI components to ensure design consistency and adherence to established standards.
- All type and interface should be defined under `types` folder with format `{entity}.type.ts`